        6
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2"
      ],
      "source": "https://www.madisonnjhistoricalsociety.org/"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "Drew University, established in 1867 on a wooded campus near downtown, remains a key educational landmark in Madison.",
